    %% External flows
    User -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token"| K8sAPI

    %% API Server to Webhook
    K8sAPI -->|"HTTPS/443->9443<br/>TLS (self-signed)<br/>API Server CA"| WebhookSvc
    WebhookSvc --> Webhook

    %% Controller flows
    K8sAPI -.->|"Watch events"| Controller
    Controller -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token"| K8sAPI

    %% Webhook flows
    Webhook -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token"| K8sAPI
    WebhookCerts -.->|"mounts"| Webhook

    %% Controller creates workloads
    Controller -->|"Creates pods,<br/>services, ingresses"| Driver
    Controller -->|"Creates"| UISvc
    Controller -->|"Creates"| ConnectSvc

    %% Driver-Executor communication
    Driver -->|"TCP/7078 driver-rpc<br/>TCP/7079 blockmanager<br/>No encryption"| Executors

    %% Spark UI access
    UIIngress -->|"HTTP/4040"| UISvc

    %% SparkConnect client access
    User -->|"gRPC/15002<br/>No encryption"| ConnectSvc

    %% Prometheus scraping
    Prometheus -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>No auth"| Controller
    Prometheus -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>No auth"| Webhook

    %% Volcano (optional)
    Controller -.->|"HTTPS/443<br/>PodGroup CRD"| Volcano

